msgid "# Minitron-8B-Base"
msgstr "# Minitron-8B-Base"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"The released `Minitron-8B-Base` is a lightweight, efficient large language "
"model developed by NVIDIA. It is designed for general-purpose text "
"generation and reasoning tasks, and can be deployed with vLLM for online "
"serving and evaluation on Ascend NPU hardware through `vllm-ascend`."
msgstr ""
"发布的 `Minitron-8B-Base` 是 NVIDIA 开发的一款轻量级、高效的大语言模型。它专为通用文本生成和推理任务设计，可通过 "
"`vllm-ascend` 在昇腾 NPU 硬件上使用 vLLM 进行在线服务部署和评估。"

msgid ""
"This document describes the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, environment preparation, single-node deployment, "
"functional verification, and accuracy evaluation on the GSM8K benchmark."
msgstr "本文档介绍了该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、环境准备、单节点部署、功能验证以及在 GSM8K 基准上的精度评估。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"`Minitron-8B-Base`(BF16 version): requires 1 Ascend 910B (with 1 x 64G "
"NPUs). [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/nv-"
"community/Minitron-8B-Base)"
msgstr ""
"`Minitron-8B-Base`（BF16 版本）：需要 1 个昇腾 910B（配备 1 x 64G "
"NPU）。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/nv-"
"community/Minitron-8B-Base)"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to place the model weight in a shared cache directory, "
"such as `/root/.cache/` or a local model path like `/data/vllm-"
"workspace/models/Minitron-8B-Base`."
msgstr ""
"建议将模型权重放置在共享缓存目录中，例如 `/root/.cache/` 或本地模型路径，如 `/data/vllm-"
"workspace/models/Minitron-8B-Base`。"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid ""
"`Minitron-8B-Base` can be deployed with `vllm-ascend` in a compatible "
"runtime environment."
msgstr "`Minitron-8B-Base` 可以在兼容的运行环境中使用 `vllm-ascend` 进行部署。"

msgid "You can use the official docker image for deployment:"
msgstr "您可以使用官方 Docker 镜像进行部署："

msgid ""
"If you do not want to use the docker image, you can also build from source:"
msgstr "如果您不想使用 Docker 镜像，也可以从源码构建："

msgid ""
"- Install `vllm-ascend` from source, refer to "
"[installation](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "- 从源码安装 `vllm-ascend`，请参考[安装指南](../../installation.md)。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "Start the online serving service with the following command:"
msgstr "使用以下命令启动在线服务："

msgid "## Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 功能验证"

msgid ""
"Once your server is started, you can query the model with a simple prompt:"
msgstr "服务器启动后，您可以使用一个简单的提示词来查询模型："

msgid ""
"A valid response indicates that the model is deployed correctly and can "
"generate text outputs."
msgstr "有效的响应表明模型已正确部署，并且能够生成文本输出。"

msgid "## Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "## 精度评估"

msgid ""
"The GSM8K dataset was used to evaluate the reasoning capability of "
"`Minitron-8B-Base`."
msgstr "使用 GSM8K 数据集评估 `Minitron-8B-Base` 的推理能力。"

msgid "The current evaluation setting is:"
msgstr "当前的评估设置为："

msgid ""
"- Dataset: `gsm8k`\n"
"- Split: `test`\n"
"- Number of samples: `1000`\n"
"- Few-shot setting: `5-shot`\n"
"- `apply_chat_template`: `False`\n"
"- `fewshot_as_multiturn`: `False`"
msgstr ""
"- 数据集：`gsm8k`\n"
"- 数据划分：`test`\n"
"- 样本数量：`1000`\n"
"- 少样本设置：`5-shot`\n"
"- `apply_chat_template`：`False`\n"
"- `fewshot_as_multiturn`：`False`"

msgid "The current evaluation results are:"
msgstr "当前的评估结果为："

msgid "### Remarks on Metrics"
msgstr "### 指标说明"

msgid ""
"- **exact_match,strict-match**: Only predictions that strictly match the expected final-answer extraction format are counted as correct.\n"
"- **exact_match,flexible-extract**: Predictions are evaluated with a more flexible answer extraction rule, which tolerates minor formatting differences as long as the final numeric answer is correct."
msgstr ""
"- **exact_match,strict-match**：仅严格匹配预期最终答案提取格式的预测才被视为正确。\n"
"- **exact_match,flexible-extract**：使用更灵活的答案提取规则评估预测，只要最终数字答案正确，可容忍细微的格式差异。"

msgid "## Performance"
msgstr "## 性能"

msgid "### Baseline Result"
msgstr "### 基线结果"

msgid ""
"`Minitron-8B-Base` can be deployed through `vllm-ascend` for online inference and benchmark evaluation.  \n"
"Actual throughput and latency depend on hardware resources, prompt length, output length, concurrency, and runtime configuration."
msgstr ""
"`Minitron-8B-Base` 可通过 `vllm-ascend` 部署用于在线推理和基准评估。  \n"
"实际吞吐量和延迟取决于硬件资源、提示词长度、输出长度、并发量和运行时配置。"

msgid "### Remarks"
msgstr "### 备注"

msgid ""
"This document focuses on functional verification and benchmark accuracy on GSM8K.  \n"
"Further benchmarking is recommended for:"
msgstr ""
"本文档侧重于功能验证和 GSM8K 上的基准精度。  \n"
"建议进一步对以下方面进行基准测试："

msgid ""
"- request latency\n"
"- throughput under concurrency\n"
"- long-context inference\n"
"- memory utilization\n"
"- stability under continuous serving workloads"
msgstr ""
"- 请求延迟\n"
"- 并发下的吞吐量\n"
"- 长上下文推理\n"
"- 内存利用率\n"
"- 持续服务负载下的稳定性"

msgid "| Category | Dataset | Metric | Result |"
msgstr "| 类别 | 数据集 | 指标 | 结果 |"
